# Transient runtime state + logs — NOT tracked. The durable record is ledger.jsonl
# (verdict chain, wg-t1-16) + audit.jsonl (dispatch history); done/ and results/ are
# superseded by the ledger. The engine mkdirs these on startup (orchestrator.py:149,185),
# so no .gitkeep is needed for a fresh clone.
running/
done/
results/
events/
events-consumed.jsonl
queue/*
!queue/.CONVENTION.md
*.log
.done-state.json
.wake-state.json
